body:
### Welcome to GitHub Pages.
This automatic page generator is the easiest way to create beautiful pages for all of your projects. Author your page content here using GitHub Flavored Markdown, select a template crafted by a designer, and publish. After your page is generated, you can check out the new branch:

### Authors and Contributors
Current authors and contributors consist of James Newhard (@newhardj) and Tyler Mobley (@mobleyt), in addition to the input and consultation of project directors (Dimitri Nakassis, Kevin Pluta).

### Support or Contact
Questions about content can be directed to James Newhard (newhardj@cofc.edu).  If you have questions specific to GitHub, contact support@github.com.
